The paper discusses a secure three-factor user authentication scheme using biometric and smart card, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the drawbacks of existing systems and proposes a new scheme that ensures high security, which could fall under the categories of cybersecurity (cs.CY), software engineering (cs.SE), information theory (cs.IT), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
